KGLhEXgO4szyg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Expresión FACIAL + sonrisa + mirada + postura","guid":"5I1Qb3A8SyCWC9loPFyteQ","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"CONTACTO FÍSICO → coger manos, acariciar","guid":"_eqrbeY6ROSMHwcXiXdU7A","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Postura RELAJADA → cercanía + confianza","guid":"lmrZrvtASi27soDPjCxndw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Tono de voz SUAVE, controlado, tranquilo","guid":"gDvQNVPRQhi7imF_beaIWg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Evitar mostrar enfado/nerviosismo","guid":"eznne8LHQbagpFtu72nATg","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"128","text":"ESCUCHA ACTIVA","guid":"E6IA_umZQgKkjJnLknvJlw","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Afirmar con cabeza","guid":"eM7R4VtOQ_q2ZvwWO4gd3g","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"Repetir mensajes importantes","guid":"_t7UZft7TFi0mAp5T6D6dA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"Preguntar sobre temas compartidos","guid":"sKEns2MtR-iRwZNrQBKOBg","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"No interrumpir, dar tiempo","guid":"AIzaFtKDQZyV2VY8DlCDTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"128","text":"COMUNICACIÓN CON DÉFICIT SENSORIAL","guid":"YOvXqXJ4ToOnxCpF_rutUw","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Verificar GAFAS/AUDÍFONO puestos","guid":"8fCwOCbLQiS1lO_CWsYByQ","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Apoyo visual con imágenes","guid":"Qe_WUX4kSbWqQIkfcZK1dA","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"Acercarse + contacto visual","guid":"vpluH8EySgaI2nCvYK0F4Q","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"Hablar despacio, vocalizar","guid":"Xha3u8izT9Oq5cR5qUeaNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"128","text":"COMUNICACIÓN CON DÉFICIT COGNITIVO","guid":"TtIOqFijSL-q_gjX_rxLdg","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"Frases simples y cortas","guid":"dFvhZQnQRW6iHFxnGFsAOQ","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"NO señalar errores ni \"no te acuerdas\"","guid":"j1aj6KAZS0erCCgPkH_mWg","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"Apoyo con imágenes/fotos","guid":"bsGzzULIS5usd3aGSKZCFg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"Tratar como adulto","guid":"s5Mtxop0SyeRq4Va3jGLrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"128","text":"ASERTIVIDAD Y MANEJO DE INFORMACIÓN","guid":"iRwuoyBKSsmKeApgogZpcg","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"PM tiene DERECHO a estar informada (diagnóstico/pronóstico/tratamiento)","guid":"C7Wdz_J6RVq5Kbrgx6hNgA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Motivar toma de decisiones propias","guid":"xoTstaF8R7WHXJgpz6OSOA","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"Evitar SOBREPROTECCIÓN","guid":"7xikd78XSgyyD3KjDC08iQ","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"En enfermedad crónica/terminal → info compartida PM + cuidador + familia + profesionales","guid":"ImN2tzKiRVWe74zgrXZSKQ","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"173","text":"TESTAMENTO VITAL / voluntades anticipadas","guid":"DXgfhKJWTYiW8P9vJExP2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"128","text":"CUANDO COMUNICACIÓN NO ES POSIBLE","guid":"gwLoJs9ZTOqb6t5tL64b2g","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"DECISIONES SUSTITUIDAS → ↑ presión en cuidador","guid":"zM_wiIsUSz6V2U62cA8y_w","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"Verificar INSTRUCCIONES PREVIAS / voluntades anticipadas","guid":"jzB4g_n5RzOqvWRYlW8YBw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"179","text":"Recordar HISTORIA DE VIDA y valores","guid":"vf5JahIuRByMiQsYNPo58w","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"179","text":"Consenso familiar + profesionales como MEDIADORES","guid":"rrlH1zgzTVKw6GEchAK4WA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"rt_MV1afSQuo-DYyrZfmDw","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"REGLA DE ORO → respetar SIEMPRE derechos, decisiones y preferencias PM","guid":"L6VcqolzQ72LPoJxLMOBxQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"CUIDADOR PRINCIPAL ≠ único cuidador → repartir carga previene claudicación","guid":"RcmsYQ_1ToyMCGGMP2FbjA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"SOBRECARGA tiene 3 dominios → FÍSICO + PSÍQUICO + SOCIAL → buscar los 3 en entrevista","guid":"4CvKg0y-Rbm06jU-mXBQ8g","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"APRENDER A DECIR NO a solicitudes no urgentes = intervención protectora contra burnout","guid":"or9MzJU_Tkqwc0isfMwT6A","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"184","text":"HUMOR + mensajes POSITIVOS (\"buena idea\" > \"no así\") mejoran adherencia > regaños en deterioro cognitivo","guid":"tDcx835KSVCrb6ywDzggzg","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"184","text":"NUNCA tratar a la PM como niño → infantilización daña autoestima y relación","guid":"niS3RqweRPywPzkgLgeUJQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"184","text":"TESTAMENTO VITAL → preguntar temprano, antes de pérdida de competencia, reduce carga decisional","guid":"tI8GC5mzSfSOL68EjzRIbQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"184","text":"Ante NEGATIVA A LA AYUDA → estrategia \"prueba\" + confianza > imposición","guid":"gy3bXOIqSvSqxKME8hQR8A","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"184","text":"AIVD son las PRIMERAS en delegarse (medicación, finanzas, transporte)","guid":"AHDQq2GYSFam0khwDqjXUg","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"184","text":"VÍNCULO CUIDADOR-PM es la red de apoyo más valorada por las PM → preservarlo es objetivo geriátrico","guid":"4WSgLvzlT6OBqhPLpYawRg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"184","text":"Referencias","guid":"Nq23Kw7QTBi7t18f48kNEw","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"1. Sociedad Española de Geriatría y Gerontología. Curso on-line para cuidadores de personas mayores en situación de dependencia. Tema 1. Madrid: SEGG; 2023. ISBN 978-84-09-47741-8.","guid":"y8pR7ccZRTaqUl6NLkAUJg","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"2. SEGG. Curso cuidadores PM dependencia. Tema 2: Cuídese para poder cuidar. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"JPDXzZSSRAisbmpxYx5FUw","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"195","text":"3. SEGG. Curso cuidadores PM dependencia. Tema 3: Relaciones y convivencia con PM en domicilio. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"vSpy6e6PSYOgftIwAXMeYw","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"195","text":"4. SEGG. Curso cuidadores PM dependencia. Tema 4: Habilidades para la comunicación. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"b6R_-KUrQsqBjTxZDGaDaA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"195","text":"5. Ballesol (colaboración). Curso SEGG cuidadores PM dependencia. 2023.","guid":"XdEnowqoTHCc_bqyxbrOOw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":200,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Cuidados-Domicilio","filename":"01-Cuidador-Bases","id":"map_929","resolved_references":[]}